title: Vita Sidorkina Absolutely Smoked Her First Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Photo Shoot
text:
TOP 5456385 
Russian model Vita Sidorkina is another one of the gorgeous girls who have joined the Sports Illustrated Swimsuit team for the 2017 issue. 
Sports Illustrated released the stunning 22-year-old supermodel’s photo shoot on Wednesday, and she absolutely rocked it. 
It might be Vita’s first appearance in Sports Illustrated Swimsuit, but it’s likely not the first time you’ve seen the blue-eyed beauty. She’s worked for several of the modeling world’s top brands and appeared in the Victoria’s Secret Fashion Show in 2015. (Photo by Dimitrios Kambouris/Getty Images for Victoria’s Secret) 
Vita grew up in the small Russian town of Khabarovsk but she knew at a young age she wanted to travel the world. Before she became a model at the age of 13, Vita wanted to be a stewardess, desperate to see the world outside of her tiny hometown. (Photo credit: JEWEL SAMAD/AFP/Getty Images) 
If Vita’s behind-the-scenes video is any indication, it looks like she’s going to make a serious splash in her Sports Illustrated Swimsuit debut. The magazine will hit news stands on February 14. (Photo by Dimitrios Kambouris/Getty Images for Victoria’s Secret)
